{
  "video_id": "XzNLfw5lS4A",
  "title": "Patrick Chappatte: The power of cartoons",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "So yeah, I&#39;m a newspaper cartoonist --"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "political cartoonist."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if you&#39;ve heard about it -- newspapers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a sort of paper-based reader."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s lighter than an iPad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a bit cheaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "You know what they say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "They say the print media is dying --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "who says that? Well, the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "But this is no news, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve read about it already."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "the world has gotten smaller."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "I know it&#39;s a cliche, but look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "look how small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "how tiny it has gotten."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "And you know the reason why, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "This is because of technology -- yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "Any computer designers in the room?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "Yeah well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "you guys are making my life miserable"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "because track pads used to be round,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "a nice round shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "That makes a good cartoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "But what are you going to do with a flat track pad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "those square things?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nothing I can do as a cartoonist."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "Well, I know the world is flat now."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "And the Internet has reached"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "every corner of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "the poorest, the remotest places."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "Every village in Africa now has a cyber cafe."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t go asking for a Frappuccino there."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "So we are bridging the digital divide."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "The Third World is connected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "we are connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "And what happens next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "Well, you&#39;ve got mail."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "Well, the Internet has empowered us."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "It has empowered you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "it has empowered me"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "and it has empowered some other guys as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "You know, these last two cartoons --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "I did them live"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "during a conference in Hanoi."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "And they were not used to that"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "in communist 2.0 Vietnam."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "So I was cartooning live on a wide screen --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "it was quite a sensation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "and then this guy came to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "He was taking pictures of me and of my sketches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "and I thought, \"This is great, a Vietnamese fan.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "And as he came the second day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"Wow, that&#39;s really a cartoon lover.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "And on the third day, I finally understood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "the guy was actually on duty."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "So by now, there must be a hundred pictures of me"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "smiling with my sketches"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "in the files of the Vietnamese police."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "No, but it&#39;s true: the Internet has changed the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "It has rocked the music industry;"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "it has changed the way we consume music."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "For those of you old enough to remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "we used to have to go to the store"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "to steal it."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "And it has changed the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "your future employer"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "will look at your application."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "So be careful"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "with that Facebook account --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "your momma told you, be careful."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "And technology has set us free --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "this is free WiFi."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "But yeah, it has liberated us"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "from the office desk."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "This is your life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "enjoy it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "In short, technology, the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "they have changed our lifestyle."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "Tech guru, like this man --"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "that a German magazine called the philosopher of the 21st century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "they are shaping the way we do things."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "They are shaping the way we consume."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "They are shaping our very desires."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "You will not like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "And technology has even changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "our relationship to God."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "Now I shouldn&#39;t get into this."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "Religion and political cartoons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "as you may have heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "make a difficult couple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "ever since that day of 2005,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "when a bunch of cartoonists in Denmark"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "drew cartoons that had repercussions all over the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "demonstrations, fatwa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "they provoked violence. People died in the violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "This was so sickening;"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "people died because of cartoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "I mean --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "I had the feeling at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "that cartoons had been used by both sides, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "They were used first by a Danish newspaper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "which wanted to make a point on Islam."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "A Danish cartoonist told me he was one of the 24"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "who received the assignment to draw the prophet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "12 of them refused. Did you know that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "He told me, \"Nobody has to tell me what I should draw."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "This is not how it works.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "And then, of course, they were used"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "by extremists and politicians on the other side."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "They wanted to stir up controversy."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "You know the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "We know that cartoons can be used as weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "History tells us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve been used by the Nazis"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "to attack the Jews."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "And here we are now."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "In the United Nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "half of the world is pushing"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "to penalize the offense to religion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "they call it the defamation of religion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "while the other half of the world is fighting back"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "in defense of freedom of speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "So the clash of civilizations is here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "and cartoons are at the middle of it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "This got me thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "Now you see me thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "at my kitchen table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "and since you&#39;re in my kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "please meet my wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "In 2006, a few months after,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "I went Ivory Coast --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "Western Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "Now, talk of a divided place -- the country was cut in two."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "You had a rebellion in the North,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "the government in the South -- the capital, Abidjan --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "and in the middle, the French army."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "This looks like a giant hamburger."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t want to be the ham in the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "I was there to report on that story"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "in cartoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been doing this for the last 15 years;"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s my side job, if you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "So you see the style is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "This is more serious than maybe editorial cartooning."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "I went to places like Gaza"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "during the war in 2009."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "So this is really journalism in cartoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll hear more and more about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "This is the future of journalism, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "And of course, I went to see the rebels in the north."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "Those were poor guys fighting for their rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "There was an ethnic side to this conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "as very often in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "And I went to see the Dozo."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "The Dozo, they are the traditional hunters"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "of West Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "People fear them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "they help the rebellion a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 477260.0,
      "text": "They are believed to have magical powers."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 477260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "They can disappear and escape bullets."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "I went to see a Dozo chief;"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "he told me about his magical powers."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I can chop your head off right away"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "and bring you back to life.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Well, maybe we don&#39;t have time for this right now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 497260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 497260.0,
      "end_time": 499260.0,
      "text": "\"Another time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 499260.0,
      "end_time": 502260.0,
      "text": "So back in Abidjan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 504260.0,
      "text": "I was given a chance to lead a workshop"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 504260.0,
      "end_time": 506260.0,
      "text": "with local cartoonists there"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "and I thought, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "in a context like this, cartoons can really be used as weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "against the other side."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "I mean, the press in Ivory Coast was bitterly divided --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "it was compared to the media in Rwanda"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 521260.0,
      "text": "before the genocide --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 521260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "so imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "And what can a cartoonist do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "Sometimes editors would tell their cartoonists"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "to draw what they wanted to see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "and the guy has to feed his family, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 533260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "So the idea was pretty simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 535260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "We brought together cartoonists"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "from all sides in Ivory Coast."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 544260.0,
      "text": "We took them away from their newspaper for three days."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 544260.0,
      "end_time": 547260.0,
      "text": "And I asked them to do a project together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 547260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "tackle the issues affecting their country"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "in cartoons, yes, in cartoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "Show the positive power of cartoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a great tool of communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "for bad or for good."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "And cartoons can cross boundaries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "as you have seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "And humor is a good way, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 568260.0,
      "text": "to address serious issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 568260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m very proud of what they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 573260.0,
      "text": "I mean, they didn&#39;t agree with each other -- that was not the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 573260.0,
      "end_time": 575260.0,
      "text": "And I didn&#39;t ask them to do nice cartoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 575260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "The first day, they were even shouting at each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 579260.0,
      "text": "But they came up with a book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 579260.0,
      "end_time": 582260.0,
      "text": "looking back at 13 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 582260.0,
      "end_time": 585260.0,
      "text": "of political crisis in Ivory Coast."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 585260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "So the idea was there."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve been doing projects like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "in 2009 in Lebanon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 594260.0,
      "text": "this year in Kenya, back in January."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 594260.0,
      "end_time": 596260.0,
      "text": "In Lebanon, it was not a book."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 596260.0,
      "end_time": 598260.0,
      "text": "The idea was to have --"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 598260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "the same principal, a divided country --"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "take cartoonists from all sides"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "and let them do something together."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "So in Lebanon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "we enrolled the newspaper editors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 610260.0,
      "text": "and we got them to publish"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 613260.0,
      "text": "eight cartoonists from all sides all together on the same page,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 613260.0,
      "end_time": 616260.0,
      "text": "addressing the issue affecting Lebanon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 619260.0,
      "text": "like religion in politics and everyday life."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "And it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 624260.0,
      "text": "For three days, almost all the newspapers of Beirut"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 626260.0,
      "text": "published all those cartoonists together --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 626260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "anti-government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 630260.0,
      "text": "pro-government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 630260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "Christian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "Muslim, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 637260.0,
      "text": "English-speaking, well, you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 637260.0,
      "end_time": 639260.0,
      "text": "So this was a great project."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 639260.0,
      "end_time": 642260.0,
      "text": "And then in Kenya, what we did"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 642260.0,
      "end_time": 644260.0,
      "text": "was addressing the issue of ethnicity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 644260.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "which is a poison in a lot of places in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "And we did video clips --"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 653260.0,
      "text": "you can see them if you go to YouTube/Kenyatoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 659260.0,
      "text": "So, preaching for freedom of speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 659260.0,
      "end_time": 661260.0,
      "text": "is easy here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 661260.0,
      "end_time": 663260.0,
      "text": "but as you have seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 663260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "in contexts of repression or division,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "again, what can a cartoonist do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 671260.0,
      "text": "He has to keep his job."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 672260.0,
      "end_time": 675260.0,
      "text": "Well I believe that in any context anywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 675260.0,
      "end_time": 677260.0,
      "text": "he always has the choice at least"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 677260.0,
      "end_time": 679260.0,
      "text": "not to do a cartoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 679260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "that will feed hatred."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 682260.0,
      "end_time": 685260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the message I try to convey to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 685260.0,
      "end_time": 688260.0,
      "text": "I think we all always have the choice in the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 688260.0,
      "end_time": 691260.0,
      "text": "not to do the bad thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 694260.0,
      "text": "But we need to support"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 694260.0,
      "end_time": 696260.0,
      "text": "these [unclear], critical"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 696260.0,
      "end_time": 699260.0,
      "text": "and responsible voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 699260.0,
      "end_time": 701260.0,
      "text": "in Africa, in Lebanon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 701260.0,
      "end_time": 704260.0,
      "text": "in your local newspaper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 704260.0,
      "end_time": 707260.0,
      "text": "in the Apple store."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "Today, tech companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "are the world&#39;s largest editors."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 715260.0,
      "text": "They decide what is too offensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 715260.0,
      "end_time": 717260.0,
      "text": "or too provocative for you to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 717260.0,
      "end_time": 720260.0,
      "text": "So really, it&#39;s not about the freedom of cartoonists;"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 720260.0,
      "end_time": 722260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about your freedoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 723260.0,
      "end_time": 726260.0,
      "text": "And for dictators all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 729260.0,
      "end_time": 731260.0,
      "text": "the good news"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 731260.0,
      "end_time": 733260.0,
      "text": "is when cartoonists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 733260.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "journalists and activists shut up."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 738260.0,
      "end_time": 740260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 740260.0,
      "end_time": 746260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}